title: Huge Baby Announcement! + Kane Brown And Nelly Talk About Their Collaboration + Raymundo Asks the Show Awkward Questions
itunes:title: Huge Baby Announcement! + Kane Brown And Nelly Talk About Their Collaboration + Raymundo Asks the Show Awkward Questions
description:
Someone comes in with a surprise baby announcement! Kane Brown stops by and brings his friend Nelly on to talk about the remix of “Cool Again” that they did together. Plus, Raymundo asks the other show members some really uncomfortable questions that listeners have been wanting to know!
